Global China Ophthalmic Service Market Insights
China Ophthalmic Service Market size was valued at USD 16.25 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 28.41 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.20% from 2024 to 2030.

China Ophthalmic Service Market Overview
The China ophthalmic service market was valued at approximately USD 16.6 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 8.2% during the forecast period. The market is driven by an increasing prevalence of eye diseases, a growing geriatric population, advancements in medical technologies, and a rising awareness about eye health. With more than 270 million people in China suffering from various eye conditions, the demand for eye care services, including surgical procedures, vision correction, and treatments for chronic conditions like cataracts and glaucoma, is expected to continue expanding. As the healthcare system evolves, private healthcare facilities and government policies are boosting investments in ophthalmic services, supporting market growth.

